<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Big Springs</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Convenient location, prime recreational activities, and availability of amenities make Big Springs an ideal place to raise children. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Big Springs Real Estate features a range of stylish homes, condos, townhouses, and apartments for both families and single individuals. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The average list price for a home for sale in Big Springs is $284,000, making it a lucrative locality for home buyers. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The green parks around the Big Springs make the neighborhood ideal for nature-lovers.</p>


